          modernInterpretation: "This is the ultimate cheat code. Krishna says if you truly KNOW — not just intellectually accept, but deeply REALIZE — that He is UNBORN (aja), WITHOUT BEGINNING (anādi), and the SUPREME LORD of all worlds, then you become 'asammūḍha' — UNDELUDED. And when delusion goes, ALL sins go with it.\n\nThink about it. Why do we sin? Because we are CONFUSED about what matters. We cheat because we think money will make us happy. We lie because we think image is everything. We hurt others because we think 'me first' is the way. ALL sin comes from DELUSION — a wrong understanding of reality. So Krishna is saying: fix the ROOT and the entire tree corrects itself.\n\nIt is like debugging code — you can fix a hundred symptoms, or you can find the ONE root cause. Knowing Krishna as the Supreme Origin is that root fix. You do not have to individually fight greed, lust, anger, jealousy. Just understand WHO is running this show, and all those bugs get auto-patched. It is the spiritual equivalent of a factory reset — but instead of losing your data, you lose your delusions. And frankly, those delusions were the REAL viruses anyway."
