          modernInterpretation: "Now the TERROR fully arrives. 'Bahu-daṁṣṭrā-karālam' — many terrible FANGS. This is no longer the gentle Krishna with the flute. This is the cosmic predator. The form that DEVOURS worlds. And Arjuna — the fearless warrior — says 'tathā aham' — SO DO I. I am trembling TOO.\n\nThe man who never trembled before ANY enemy on the battlefield is shaking before this vision. Because this is not an enemy you can fight. This is REALITY showing its full face — and reality has TEETH.\n\nThis is the honest truth about encountering the Absolute. It is not all flowers and incense. It has a TERRIFYING side. The same ocean that gives you beautiful sunsets can drown you. The same God who cradles you can CONSUME you."
