          transliteration: "ye tu sarvāṇi karmāṇi mayi sannyasya mat-parāḥ |\nananyenaiva yogena māṁ dhyāyanta upāsate ||6||\nteṣām ahaṁ samuddhartā mṛtyu-saṁsāra-sāgarāt |\nbhavāmi na cirāt pārtha mayy āveśita-cetasām ||7||",
