          translation: "That knowledge by which one sees a single imperishable reality in all beings — undivided among the divided — know that knowledge to be sattvic.",
          modernInterpretation: "SATTVIC knowledge — the highest form of understanding. It is the ability to see ONE undivided, imperishable REALITY in ALL the diverse beings around you. The dog, the professor, the tree, the billionaire, the beggar — all different on the OUTSIDE, but containing the same INDESTRUCTIBLE consciousness on the inside.\n\nThis is like understanding that every device in the world — iPhone, Android, laptop, smart TV — is running on ELECTRICITY. The devices look completely different, have different brands, different prices, different capabilities. But the ENERGY that powers them all is the same. Sattvic knowledge is seeing the ENERGY, not just the devices.\n\nWhen a scientist looks at the periodic table, they see that all matter — from gold to garbage — is made of the same fundamental particles, just ARRANGED differently. That is sattvic scientific knowledge. When a spiritual person looks at humanity, they see that all people — saints and sinners — contain the same divine spark, just EXPRESSED differently. That is sattvic spiritual knowledge. The word AVIBHAKTAM is powerful — UNDIVIDED. The reality itself was NEVER divided. Only our perception creates divisions. Sattvic knowledge heals that false perception."
